n these peaks being not less than 10. System repeatability: When the test is repeated 5 times with 10 mL of the standard solution under the above operat-ing conditions, the relative standard deviation of the ratios of the peak area of loxoprofen to that of the internal stand-ard is not more than 1.0z."
